%h1 Confirmed gifts

- if @confirmed and !@confirmed.empty?
  .info These are gifts which people have confirmed their intention of purchasing, but haven't finalised by clicking the link in the email they were sent.
  %br

  - @confirmed.each do |gift|
    .box
      %a{:href => "/gift/#{gift.id}/edit", :style => "float: right;"}= "edit"
      %h2= gift.name
      .description= gift.description
      .info
        ="Confirmed by #{gift.intention.name} (#{gift.intention.email})"
- else
  %p No gifts currently in a confirmed state.